{"tid":2157751,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警方拘 26 歲警務處文職人員　疑上載內部文件至連登討論區","createTime":"2020-08-15T08:49:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T09:04:44.000Z","uid":262250,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f655512a5563daa4e14b2f71c28bdbedddedb21e","tid":2157751,"uid":262250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T08:49:53.000Z","msg":"反送中運動以來，網上不時傳出警隊內部消息。警方今日（14 日）晚上發稿，指網絡安全及科技罪案調查科主動介入調查，一宗涉及文職人員的有犯罪或不誠實意圖而取用電腦案。經調查後，警方於 8 月 12 日拘捕一名 26 歲文職人員，涉嫌自去年 8 月至今，多次於一個網上討論區上載警方內部文件。據警方消息指，涉案人員是將文件上載到「連登討論區」，消息又指有關文職人員是從政府資訊科技總監辦公室，借調到警務處的「IT文職人員」。<br />\n<br />\n該名被捕男子已獲准保釋候查，須於 8 月下旬向警方報到，而他亦已被停職等候進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示警隊非常重視人員操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3359426640809599/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F3359426640809599%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8bc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=d20e840d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3359426640809599/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"133202cf9c8fae0bca97c1a7b6bbfa8c58bbfc78","tid":2157751,"uid":262250,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T08:50:34.000Z","msg":"好似唔見有人講"},{"pid":"89d0606f49beb21249233be34b5db78878ae3b47","tid":2157751,"uid":262250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T08:51:14.000Z","msg":"係咪鳩sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c3213ea82a41c25aa81593483939ff5093044e5","tid":2157751,"uid":128102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T08:52:20.000Z","msg":"鳩sir報左平安未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n你點衰的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c65e14e456fa669311b4370a7a4086365e638f4","tid":2157751,"uid":199893,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T08:52:45.000Z","msg":"警方表示警隊非常重